    "Id": "chassisdef_kumazemi_KUZ-C3",
    "Name": "Kumazemi",
    "Details": "The KUZ-C3 refines the original Kumazemi's loadout with a trio of practical upgrades. The head-mounted Machine Gun has been replaced with a Small Laser for ammunition independent close defense, an SRM-6 has been added to the left torso for additional short range punch, and single heat sinks have given way to double heat sinks throughout. Together, these changes allow the KUZ-C3 to sustain heavier fire from its AC/20 and LRM-15 while adding a meaningful close-combat option its predecessor lacked.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Rugged</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.14</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Lower, Right Lower</color>",
